What you need is just some magazines and a roll of duct tape .
Just place the magazines over potential "bite prone" areas such as shoulders, arms, legs and around the torso.
Tape em shut and go.

It probably won't keep you save from a horde but it will at least potentially save you from one or two gnawers who managed to sneak up on you.
